{"tid":1254979,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做乜要分化父母同仔女","createTime":"2019-06-24T10:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T11:22:56.000Z","uid":10451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f6149870e81247c8c4401625440f114b6f7069a","tid":1254979,"uid":10451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/258297580954840/posts/2183172111800701?s=583478433&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F258297580954840%2Fposts%2F2183172111800701%3Fs%3D583478433%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVCSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=d13f9180\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/258297580954840/posts/2183172111800701?s=583478433&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱睇到呢條片我覺得講得幾好，唔理係藍定黃，父母就係父母，子女就係子女。父母同仔女之間嘅關係冇可能因為政見而變質。互相尊重，就係大家最和諧嘅相處。<br />\n<br />\n我自己亦都係同我父母有不同政見，係呢幾日嘅時事話題上，我總會留一口，讓大家好下台，畢竟親情比政治更切身，值得去珍惜，要互相尊重。雖然到現在我都未有能力改變父母立場，但最起碼我們之間關係沒有變差，而又各自正確表達自己意見。"},{"pid":"48eac63e3cbc6fe0f4cdfdc8e78533822352d923","tid":1254979,"uid":92273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"推 !"},{"pid":"1472093673c2a74622dadb24ce7119edfa8fe771","tid":1254979,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}